ta-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeZJvtvt.png&h=8b4acb23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PJXwcW9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPJXwcW9.png&h=d3f530ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9jeuJ3R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9jeuJ3R.png&h=afacc126&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:11:01.000Z","msg":"匈牙利景點都係集中係布達佩斯？除左有無值得去既景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec0f8c2ba852be81576cddc75f154f8e789da4fe","tid":972144,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:12:09.000Z","msg":"Grand Budapest <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b64859595240f3c3a91662161d720d1ca290ed7b","tid":972144,"uid":55739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T08:58:42.000Z","msg":"匈牙利首都 Budapest既景點好靚 野食都係我去左歐洲幾個地方（法/西/德/波/意）最好食 <br />\n成個set dinner starter 係鵝肝 2個人都係400有找 平香港多多聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲記得有一餐佢個starter係羅宋湯 （佢地隻羅宋湯又唔係exactly香港果隻）有好多牛肉 飲完已經飽左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我果陣去左3日2夜 1日full day 新城 1日full day舊城甘樣 因為景點同景點間都幾密 但有少少chur既<br />\n<br />\n佢既夜景真係好靚好靚   夜晚睇佢個國會大樓同白色個城堡（唔記得咩名）真係好靚 真心同巴黎鐵塔有得揮  <br />\n如果去白色個城堡一定要記得去埋佢附近個地下博物館  （佢個門口好on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全唔似博物館）<br />\n個博物館好似係由咩地牢改成 傳說德古拉伯爵都比佢困左係到一排 入到去其實係黑到仆街既迷宮黎 真係黑到伸手不見五指 佢會比盞油燈你照住黎行 愛有feel 之後成個博物館整到好撚恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  會有好多監獄入面有假人像 再播住好陰森既音樂 有個位仲係整左個假德古拉伯爵個監獄 附近有人頭 好撚好玩"},{"pid":"4947d324460481083f2bab9e9fb2de64195e1cdf","tid":